 We will start by declaring two array left_to_right and right_to_left
First we will travel from left to right fillling our array with the number of candy we are giving to ith child..Now here we need to see the child with more rating should get more candy than their neighbour we satisfied this for left neighbour but we need to check for right neighbour also maybe they have more candy so we need to update it accordingly..You would have used only single array and updated that but creating different array gives more clear idea. We wil travel form right to left and will fill the another array satisfying the condition given in que. After it for each index we will take max from both array as we need to make sure higher rating child get higher candy compared to its both left and rightr neighbour./

