We first evaluated price when each item/needs is bought individually. This is our current cost. 
Now for each offer first check if offer is valid or not. Offer is only valid if it has all the item <= needs. If an offer is valid take the offer and recursively check for price of rest of needs. Map(cache) is used to cache result .

